                     <interp inst="t17700117-18-person254" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in Guildhall. I saw the prisoner take the prosecutor's neckcloath out of his pocket, and put it into his breeches. I told the prosecutor of it; and took it myself out of his breeches. (produced and deposed to.)</p>
